        <heading>Conspicuous language on the face of certificates</heading>
        <content>
          <p>ยง 1709. Conspicuous language on the face of certificates.\n  All certificates representing shares of a benefit corporation shall\ncontain, in addition to any other statements required by the business\ncorporation law, the following conspicuous language on the face of the\ncertificate:\n  "This entity is a benefit corporation organized under article\nseventeen of the New York business corporation law."\n</p>
        </content>
